{{defn|no= 2|defn= (of a flowering plant) The period during which flowers in [[#anthesis|anthesis]] are present. Not defined for some cases, such as when pollen is released in the bud.}}

{{term|term= anthophore |content= anthophore }}
{{defn|defn=A stalk-like structure, internode located between the calyx and the other parts of the flower.}}

{{term|term= anticlinal |content= anticlinal }}
