{{term|term= bryophyte |content= [[bryophyte]] }}
{{defn|defn= Informally, a collective term for the [[moss]]es, [[hornwort]]s and [[liverwort]]s. Formally, these plants are placed in three separate divisions: hornworts ([[Anthocerophyta]]), liverworts ([[Marchantiophyta]]) and mosses ([[Moss|Bryophyta]]).}}

{{term|term= bulb |content= [[bulb]] }}
