{{defn|defn= of a fruit, when it [[#dehisce|dehisces]] through the centres of [[#locule|loculi]]. Compare [[#septicidal|septicidal]].}}

{{term|term= locule |content= [[locule]] }}
{{defn|defn= a chamber or cavity containing seeds within an [[#ovary|ovary]], pollen within an [[#anther|anther]] or spores in a [[#sporangium|sporangium]]. }}

{{term|term= lodicule |content= [[lodicule]] }}
{{defn|defn= one of 2 or three minute organs at the base of the [[#ovary|ovary]] of a [[grass]] flower, representing parts of a strongly reduced [[#perianth|perianth]].}}

{{term|term= lomentum |content= [[lomentum]] }}
{{defn|defn= a pod-like indehiscent fruit that develops constrictions between the segments and at maturity breaks into one-seeded segments.}}

{{term|term= longicidal |content= [[longicidal]] }}
{{defn|defn= (anthers) opening lengthwise by longitudinal slits. compare: [[#poricidal|poricidal]]}}

{{term|term= lunate |content= [[lunate]] }}
{{defn|defn= crescent-shaped.}}

{{term|term= lumen }}
{{defn|defn= the cavity bounded by a plant cell wall.}}

{{term|term= lyrate |content= [[lyrate]] }}
{{defn|defn= lyre-shaped; deeply lobed, with a large terminal lobe and smaller lateral ones.}}

{{glossary end}}


