{{defn|no=2|defn= in Camellias the final [[#bract|bracts]] and sepals become indistinguishable and are called perules.}}
{{defn|no=3|defn= a kind of sac formed by the adherent bases of the two lateral sepals in certain orchids.}}

{{term|term= petal |content= [[petal]] }}
