{{term|term= placodioid |content= [[placodioid]] }}
{{defn|defn= The form of a lichen [[thallus]] which radiates outward with the ends of the radiating arms peeling up from the substrate, but which lack a cortex on the underside (unlike [[#foliose|foliose]] lichens).}}

